title: KLM Travel Watch Face
summary: Do you love to travel? Fan of airplanes? Let KLM watchfaces inspire you!

descriptionHTML:
Choose your watchface:
1. The inspirational watchface shows you pictures of destinations where we can take you to.
2. Do you like to fly skyhigh? KLM has a very cool aviator watchface for you.
3. Are you more into aviation? The KLM Airplane watchface shows you great pictures of planes, engines and more!

You can also download the KLM app for smartwatch via the Google Play store for smartphones.
comments: Geweldig! Zeer mooie watchface,  maar het zou nog mooier zijn als de altitude meter met de G watch R echt zou werken!!
Super Gaaf dat KLM een eigen wijzerplaat voor smartwatches heeft!
KLM the plane that you can trust.
Splendid! What a great idea KLM! I really enjoy this app quality and display!
